the last two syllables are entirely conjectural; in the context of karma and vacaḥ, one also things of the triad deed-speech-thought, and so we might have manaḥ instead of 'vatu, though I feel we need a verb.
--> <lb n="B4"/><seg met="+-="><gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/></seg> <g type="ddanda">.</g></l>
